<div class="container">
  <div class="what_is">
    <h3>What is GiftHorse?</h3>

    <p>It's about giving. Through connectivity and simplicity, GiftHorse connects the dots and bridges the gap
      between the idea of giving and the act of making it all happen , allowing users to easily send gifts to
      friends and loved ones.</p>
    <p>By collecting items you like, friends and family members can easily browse items in your list, and the next time
    a special occasion arrives, giving will be easier than ever.  For you, and for them. </p>

    <p>
      For every gift we send for you, GiftHorse donates to Child's Dream, a non-profit dedicated
      to empowering marginalised children and youth in Myanmar, Laos, Thailand and Cambodia.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="login">
    <h3>Login</h3>

    <%= form_tag sessions_path do %>

      <p>
        <%= label_tag :username, "Username", class: "form-label" %>
        <%= text_field_tag :username %>
      </p>

      <p>
        <%= label_tag :password, "Password", class: "form-label" %>
        <%= password_field_tag :password %>
      </p>

      <p class="sign_in">
        <%= submit_tag "Login", class: "form-button" %>
      </p>
      <p class="flash_notice_login"><%= flash[:alert] %></p>

    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="create_account">

    <h3>Create An Account</h3>

    <%= form_for @user do |f| %>

      <% if @user.errors.present? %>
        <div class="errors">
          <ul class="error-list">
            <% @user.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
              <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      <% end %>


      <p>
        <%= f.label :username, class: "form-label" %>
        <%= f.text_field :username %>
      </p>

      <p>
        <%= f.label :password, class: "form-label" %>
        <%= f.password_field :password %>
      </p>

      <p class="create">
        <%= f.submit "Create Account", class: "form-button" %>
      </p>

      <p><% if flash[:notice] %><p>
        <p class="flash_notice_created"><%= flash[:notice] %></p>
      <% end %>
      </p>

    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>




